    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm just really worried about a low. if i only ate like 100 calories, wouldn't my body just need way less insulin for the night? it feels safer to just skip it than to risk a hypoglycemic episode while i'm asleep and can't react.",
